 - DTLX group: done ✅\nSystem: - 2 stale zombies: running (pre-existing)\nSystem: \nSystem: **Current state (14:06 UTC):** All identical — same 3 cron sessions running, same done sessions, same zombies. No new failures, no blockers, no new sessions.\nSystem: \nSystem: **No changes detected. Silent exit.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 14:09:43 UTC] Silent exit — no changes detected.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 14:12:33 UTC] Silent exit — no changes detected since last heartbeat (13:36 UTC).\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 2:14 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 14:14 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776176078211,"__openclaw":{"id":"4d8526d3","seq":122}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same routine - 3 cron sessions active, pipeline stable, no changes. Silent exit."},{"type":"text","text":"\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1452,"output":27,"totalTokens":72627,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":71148,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776176078631,"responseId":"062d7ed0eb18a2fb212721eff45c800f","__openclaw":{"id":"9546f8d4","seq":123}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:b653a6c0-143b-4b53-a242-034bc5fd9fca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Orbis QLHV Report 11:53 UTC","displayName":"Cron: Orbis QLHV Report 11:53 UTC","updatedAt":1776167853466,"sessionId":"2f8d61ea-217f-4a52-8c6b-32e142e69caf","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2f8d61ea-217f-4a52-8c6b-32e142e69caf.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:c